{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/use-the-text-transform-property-to-make-text-uppercase","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"applied-visual-design","demoType":null,"title":"Koristi text-transform svojstvo da tekst bude velikim slovima","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><code>text-transform</code> svojstvo u CSS-u sluzi za promenu izgleda teksta. To je jednostavan nacin da obezbedite dosledan prikaz teksta na stranici, bez menjanja stvarnog tekstualnog sadrzaja HTML elemenata.</p>\n<p>Tabela ispod prikazuje kako razlicite <code>text-transform</code> vrednosti menjaju primer teksta \"Transform me\".</p>\n<table><thead><tr><th>Vrednost</th><th>Rezultat</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>lowercase</code></td><td>\"transform me\"</td></tr><tr><td><code>uppercase</code></td><td>\"TRANSFORM ME\"</td></tr><tr><td><code>capitalize</code></td><td>\"Transform Me\"</td></tr><tr><td><code>initial</code></td><td>Koristi podrazumevanu vrednost</td></tr><tr><td><code>inherit</code></td><td>Koristi <code>text-transform</code> vrednost roditeljskog elementa</td></tr><tr><td><code>none</code></td><td><strong>Podrazumevano:</strong> Koristi originalni tekst</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</section>","id":"587d781c367417b2b2512ac0","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Promenite <code>h4</code> tekst u velika slova koristeci <code>text-transform</code> svojstvo.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/c/cvVZQSP","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301081,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/use-the-text-transform-property-to-make-text-uppercase"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\n  h4 {\n    text-align: center;\n    background-color: rgba(45, 45, 45, 0.1);\n    padding: 10px;\n    font-size: 27px;\n\n  }\n  p {\n    text-align: justify;\n  }\n  .links {\n    text-align: left;\n    color: black;\n    opacity: 0.7;\n  }\n  #thumbnail {\n    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.19), 0 6px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.23);\n  }\n  .fullCard {\n    width: 245px;\n    border: 1px solid #ccc;\n    border-radius: 5px;\n    margin: 10px 5px;\n    padding: 4px;\n  }\n  .cardContent {\n    padding: 10px;\n  }\n  .cardText {\n    margin-bottom: 30px;\n  }\n</style>\n<div class=\"fullCard\" id=\"thumbnail\">\n  <div class=\"cardContent\">\n    <div class=\"cardText\">\n      <h4>Alphabet</h4>\n      <hr>\n      <p><em>Google was founded by Larry Page and Sergey Brin while they were <u>Ph.D. students</u> at <strong>Stanford University</strong>.</em></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"cardLinks\">\n      <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Larry_Page\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"links\">Larry Page</a><br><br>\n      <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sergey_Brin\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"links\">Sergey Brin</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>h4</code> tekst treba da bude <code>uppercase</code>.</p>","testString":"const h4Element =document.querySelector('h4')\nconst h4Style = window.getComputedStyle(h4Element);\nassert.equal(h4Style?.textTransform, 'uppercase');"},{"text":"<p>Originalni <code>h4</code> tekst ne treba da bude izmenjen.</p>","testString":"assert.notEqual(document.querySelector('h4')?.textContent, document.querySelector('h4')?.textContent?.toUpperCase());"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#applied-visual-design","dashedName":"use-the-text-transform-property-to-make-text-uppercase","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":fa